Text: A California federal judge has granted Warner Bros.' motion for a temporary restraining order on Age of the Hobbits, a low-budget movie the studio contends is confusingly similar to its own Peter Jackson blockbuster The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey, which opens Dec. 14.
